title: Dubai traffic alert today: Major road closures announced for UAE Tour Women 2026
summary_full: Dubai gears up to host the UAE Tour Women 2026's second stage this Friday, February 6. Cyclists will traverse iconic city routes, leading to brief, rolling road closures for 10-15 minutes.  Motorists are advised to plan ahead for temporary disruptions as the emirate showcases its commitment to women's cycling and recreational sports.
